  02 Jan 2013; Andreas Schuerch <nativemad@gentoo.org> passenger-3.0.17.ebuild:
  x86 stable, see bug 440098

  27 Nov 2012; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Drop apache herd as discussed in http://www.gossamer-
  threads.com/lists/gentoo/dev/262834

  24 Nov 2012; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org>
  files/30_mod_passenger-2.0.1.conf:
  Specify /usr/bin/ruby as the interpreter since this will work in most cases
  where people have a single RUBY_TARGET.

